@berryma4 I don't think the Date rolling policy will take affect any longer since the files now roll based on size. Unless I'm missing something I don't believe DatePattern actually has any affect on the DailyFileAppender. 

http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/apidocs/org/apache/log4j/RollingFileAppender.html

I haven't tried this out but including it will likely cause a WARN or ERROR message to be thrown since the RollingFileAppender is not aware of the DatePattern.
